snippet.title: Best VGM 2120 - Star Fox Adventures - Snowhorn Wastes
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 424 - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hyjJl59f_I0

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Snowhorn Wastes
